Quickstrike:




Quickstrike glared at Mantella. "Jus' bang'd mah head, ev'rybody does it." 
He looked away, feeling a little embarassed that she had caught him in the 
action of a clumsy manuver. "Could use ya fer some back up, is all. Don't 
really trust no body 'round here. Shredder's actin' all high an' mighty, an' 
ah don't trust those others with Hell Beast. Don't trust none of them." He 
studied her hard. "Ya might be th' only one ah do trust. 'Cept Taransulas. 
He's got somethin' brewin' on his brain." He shrugged. "Don't know what it 
is. Trust me?"
